---
title: Grilled Maple Pork Chops with Smashed Potatoes and Spring Salad
description: Fire up the BBQ and get ready for perfectly-grilled pork chops, smothered in a spicy maple sauce! We've paired them with a crisp salad and dreamy creamy mashed potatoes for a summer-inspired feast!
